column1: Daily Weather Observations for Millendon (Swan Valley), Western Australia for January 2024
Prepared at 13:02 UTC on Wednesday  3 April 2024   IDCJDW6005.202401
Most observations from Millendon in the Swan Valley, but some from Perth Airport.
Perth Airport is about 13 km to the south of Millendon.
Temperature, humidity, wind, pressure and rainfall observations are from Millendon (Swan Valley) {station 009281}
Cloud, evaporation and sunshine observations are from Perth Airport {station 009021}
